  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contact.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- About Me Section -->
  <section id="about-me">
    <div class="about-content">
      <!-- Top Row -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="image green-circle">
          <img src="/images/green-circle.png" alt="Creative Workflow">
        </div>
        <div class="text-block">
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent commodo.</p>
          <p>Phasellus sit amet justo vel odio consequat tincidunt et eu orci.</p>
          <p>Sed scelerisque, nulla in suscipit gravida, orci risus fermentum libero.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!-- Bottom Row -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="text-block">
          <p>Mauris nec dolor id quam ultricies placerat eget et libero.</p>
          <p>Curabitur malesuada risus ac nulla sollicitudin, sed dictum risus faucibus.</p>
          <p>Ut faucibus ligula in sapien luctus, nec bibendum sapien auctor.</p>
        </div>
